WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.570 align:middle line:10%
>> On a new episode
of "Crystals"--

00:00:04.570 --> 00:00:07.930 align:middle line:10%
>> Each crystal has a special
gift to offer and can be

00:00:07.930 --> 00:00:11.530 align:middle line:10%
utilized to become a personal
power piece that will assist

00:00:11.530 --> 00:00:14.440 align:middle line:10%
its user in attaining
certain states of awareness

00:00:14.440 --> 00:00:17.410 align:middle line:10%
or achieving specific goals.

00:00:17.410 --> 00:00:19.480 align:middle line:10%
>> This week, on Gaia--

00:00:19.480 --> 00:00:24.100 align:middle line:10%
>> We can work with crystals
to aid us in our dream time.

00:00:24.100 --> 00:00:26.037 align:middle line:84%
We can use crystals
to help us ground,

00:00:26.037 --> 00:00:28.120 align:middle line:84%
because almost all crystals
are going to be coming

00:00:28.120 --> 00:00:31.180 align:middle line:90%
from that Mother Earth energy.

00:00:31.180 --> 00:00:33.280 align:middle line:84%
>> On "Beyond Belief
with George Noory"--

00:00:33.280 --> 00:00:36.610 align:middle line:84%
>> I had to disappoint my ego
and go truly into my heart

00:00:36.610 --> 00:00:38.380 align:middle line:90%
space and find my passion.

00:00:38.380 --> 00:00:41.500 align:middle line:10%
And my soul realized
that I had this purpose

00:00:41.500 --> 00:00:46.660 align:middle line:10%
to be able to help people find
their path by understanding

00:00:46.660 --> 00:00:48.520 align:middle line:10%
who they really are.

00:00:48.520 --> 00:00:51.520 align:middle line:10%
>> On "Open Minds with
Regina Meredith"--

00:00:51.520 --> 00:00:53.830 align:middle line:10%
>> When we have
our voices heard,

00:00:53.830 --> 00:00:58.090 align:middle line:10%
whether we're speaking out or
we're voting in a certain way,

00:00:58.090 --> 00:01:03.505 align:middle line:10%
whatever we do has the
ability to make the change.

